body: * Fix: fatal error with User Switching plugin – firing `wp_login` too early. Fix #24, thanks @sisaacrussell, @johnbillion, @mgratch

name: v2.4.1
body: * Fix: fatal error with WooCommerce HPOS meta boxes hook – strict typing issue. Fix #25 Thanks @sisaacrussell. See https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-private-uploads/commit/d9f362b2ef7aa7818791e82aad4e0cf5c686ef82

name: v2.4.0
body:
* Add: REST API
* Add/fix: prefill WooCommerce checkout with user details from The Newsletter Plugin, Klaviyo, Mailpoet
* Fix: fatal error on first request after WooCommerce is deleted from filesystem
* Fix: broken WooCommerce orders page
* Fix: strpos() null error when HTTP_USER_AGENT missing. Thanks @sisaacrussell
* Fix: [bug with bh-wp-logger](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-logger/commit/43515b654781e38b30523fe0ae4e2ba9ab909271) – thanks @sisaacrussell
* Improve: logging
* Improve: don't add autologin codes to The Newsletter Plugin emails' URLs

name: v2.3.0
body: * Add: "Send magic login email" button on users list table * Fix: [bug with bh-wp-logger](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-logger/commit/7bfd66b74e355d2832c45c4056b964fd75c797f2) – thanks @Amit-Biswas * Add: screenshots to .org plugin page * Add: CLI documentation * Fix: minor wording * Dev: add Playwright tests

name: v2.2.0
body:
* Add: configurable template for `user-edit.php` autologin URL
* Add: `user-edit.php` autologin URL click to copy to clipboard
* Fix: "Email Magic Link" on `wp-login.php` was disabled when Firefox autofilled the username
* Fix: JS for logs page were excluded from the plugin archive

![bh-wp-autologin-urls-user-edit-template-clipboard](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-autologin-urls/assets/4720401/9f5d3799-e56f-404a-8248-68d1c37dd5b4)

name: v2.1.1
body:
* Fix: Default expiry time when omitted in CLI was parsing as 0
* Add: Warning that logs may contain autologin codes

name: v2.1.0
body:
* Add: CLI commands `wp autologin-urls get-url` and `wp autologin-urls send-magic-link`
* Fix: Links to `/wp-admin` were redirecting to wp-login screen because `$_COOKIE` was not yet set
* Performance: Return early when no querystring set
* Fix: `wp_safe_redirect()` `exit()` is now conditional

name: v2.0.0
body:
* Breaking: UI for regex subject filters removed (functionality still exists through filters)
* Fix: Use correct `determine_current_user` filter for login
* Update library: RateLimit library has bugfix to handle `false` returned from transients for expected `array`
* Update library: bh-wp-logger library has performance and feature improvements

name: v1.10.0
body:
* Add `bh_wp_autologin_urls_should_delete_code_after_use` filter
* Improved logging

name: v1.9.0
body:
* Add: checkbox to enable/disable magic links
* Add: magic link button on WooCommerce checkout
* Add: enable overriding the settings page template
* Improve: logging
* Dev: use [Alley Interactive autoloader](https://github.com/alleyinteractive/wordpress-autoloader)

name: v1.8.0
body:
* Add: ignore requests from bots (check HTTP_USER_AGENT for "bot") to avoid expiring codes when Outlook.com crawls the URL
* Fix: do not redirect_to wp-login.php, unwrap the inner redirect_to and use that
* Fix: unprefixed Klaviyo\ApiException.

name: v1.7.1
body: * Fix: set content type on HTML emails * Fix: do not generate autologin URLs when serving WC_Orders over REST API * Improve: hyperlinks in log table

name: v1.7.0
body: * Add: Magic-link emails on wp-login.php and WooCommerce login forms * Add: Git Updater * Improved PHPCS and logging

name: v1.6.3
body:
* Fix: Catch Klaviyo API errors
* Language: Include generated .pot file

name: v1.6.2
body: * Update logger library for performance

name: v1.6.1
body:
* Fix: Fatal error when Klaviyo querystring was defined but empty
* Fix: fatal error when `plugin_action_links_{}` filter called with null as parameter values (Jetpack)
* Fix: (temp) Error when WooCommerce shuts down due to virtual WC_Customer
* Fix: error when wp_mail's $to is an array

name: v1.6.0
body: * Add: Links to Settings and Logs on plugin install confirmation page * Fix: Prefilling WooCommerce customer data when no WP_User available: missing function parameter, wc_get_orders called too soon

name: v1.5.0
body:
* Add: Support for using [Klaviyo](https://www.klaviyo.com/) tracking links as autologin links
* Change: Use library [nikolaposa/rate-limit](https://github.com/nikolaposa/rate-limit) for rate limiting rather than internal code
* Add: interface for integrations
* Fix: Return early when user is already logged in
* Fix: Error when [Guzzle not prefixed](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/strauss/issues/44)
* Dev: Project structure changed

name: v1.4.0
body:
* Add: On admin UI single order page, add the autologin code to the "Customer payment page" link (w/ copy-to-clipboard)
* Security: Exclude emails with multiple recipients @TimothyBJacobs

name: v1.3.3
body:
* Use custom table for storing codes, because [transients are too ephemeral](https://journal.rmccue.io/296/youre-using-transients-wrong/) – thanks @rmccue
* Option to bounce users through wp-login.php, to avoid caching issues – thanks @bradyvercher
* Logs users in from links in [The Newsletter Plugin](https://wordpress.org/plugins/newsletter/)
* Logs users in from links in [MailPoet](https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailpoet/)
* Prefill WooCommerce checkout data for mailing list users without accounts
* More secure verification via [`hash_equals`](https://www.php.net/manual/en/function.hash-equals.php) – thanks @timothyBJacobs
* Rate limiting bad login attempts
* [Logging](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-logger) (mostly off by default)

A lot of this was written in 2020. I'm a bit slow getting it unit tested and released.

There are still some changes from feedback to be implemented.

The [logging library](https://github.com/BrianHenryIE/bh-wp-logger) is still beta, so I won't push this to [WordPress.org](https://wordpress.org/plugins/bh-wp-autologin-urls/) yet.
Now using Composer Mozart to nest dependency namespaces within the project namespace.

name: Rate-limiting
body:
Plugin now rate-limits assumed bad actors.
